data.description: Check out this incredible, move in ready 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath brick Tri-level. Seller has invested in a long list of updates and improvements. This home rests on a large 260x100 lot with brick paver sidewalks and driveway leading up to the 2 car attached garage. Spend your summers entertaining and relaxing in your own back yard oasis. Cool off swimming in the inground pool with diving board or soak up the rays laying out on the spacious deck, all surrounded by a privacy fence. Or de-stress year round in your hot tub located in the the screened in 3 season room conveniently located between kitchen and back yard. Gas fireplace in the lower level family room.
